<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Vimberlin</h1>
    <p>Our goal is to bring new and trained people using Vim together to talk about their practices, tools, and their habits working with Vim. If you want to <strong>give a talk</strong> (either a short 5 minute presentation or a longer one), please post your proposal on our <a href="https://groups.google.com/group/vimberlin/">mailing list</a> or ping us on <a href="https://twitter.com/vimberlin">twitter</a>.
</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h2>Latest posts</h2>
      <% blog.articles[0...5].each do |article| %>
        <article>
          <h4>
            <a href="<%= article.url %>"><%= article.title %></a>
            <time><%= article.date.strftime('%b %e %Y') %></time>
          </h4>
        </article>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <% 3.times do %>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4>Section Title</h4>
        <p><%= greek 200 %></p>
        <p><a href="" class="btn btn-default">Read More</a></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
